cast.overview: A young pregnant woman named Mia escapes from a country at war by hiding in a maritime container aboard a cargo ship. After a violent storm, Mia gives birth to the child while lost at sea, where she must fight to survive.
cast.title: Nowhere

details.biography: Mariam Torres has been educated by several techniques of theatre and audiovisual acting. She has been educated in theatre by Shakesapeare Foundation (Valencia 2011), M. A. Conejero and continuing by the profesional coaching Fernando Piernas (Madrid 2012) and Macarena  Pombo. Graduated by Central de Cine  (Madrid 2012)  in acting in CINEMA and TV.﻿
details.name: Mariam Torres
